				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-2913401#post-3337343</guid>
				<title>(no title)</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-2913401/scp-3071#post-3337343</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Tue, 18 Jul 2017 12:44:20 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>Lex1nat0r</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>2172650</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>Novote from me, there just isn't enough detail to actually grab me here. The effect is scary, and becomes genuinely terrifying after the unpredictable expansion after the first figure leaves the cabin but that becomes a nonissue given that it gets neutralized in the addendum.</p> <p>Speaking of the addendum, the line</p> <blockquote> <p>SCP-3071-1 reportedly had a conversation about [REDACTED] with Dr. Alexander Raedon</p> </blockquote> <p>really makes me bounce off the article. I wasn't able to pick up on any hints that would let me figure out what's behind that [REDACTED], so I'm just kind of left hanging and don't really get a good payoff.</p> <p>And it might be worthwhile to provide a transcript of the letter. The font's a little tricky to read.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
